div.padding.light(style="padding-top: 6rem")
  div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
    //- :Left
  
  //- Contents
  div.card.padding-medium.margin
    h2 Calendar
    table.wide
      tr
        td Block Days of the Week
        td
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Sun
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Mon
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Tue
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Wed
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Thu
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Fri
          label
            input(type="checkbox")
            span Sat
      tr
        td Block Specific Dates
        td
          input(type="date")
          button Block
          table
            tr
              td December 25, 2018
              td: button X
        
  
  div
    button.float-right Discard
    button.float-right Save Changes


  modal(ref="newaddon" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding New Addon
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            form.flex.column
              label Addon Type
              select
                option Fake Type
              label Description
              input
              label Price
              input
              label Max. Quantity
              input
              label
                input(type='checkbox')
                span Active
              div
                button Cancel
                button Create Addon

  modal(ref="editaddon" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Edit Addon
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            form.flex.column
              label Addon Type
              select
                option Fake Type
              label Description
              input
              label Price
              input
              label Max. Quantity
              input
              label
                input(type='checkbox')
                span Active
              div
                button Delete
                button Update Addon
